    <h2 class="about-h1">What&rsquo;s This All About</h2>
    <p class="aboutText-p">Be Brave Podcast is a collaboration between childhood friends; designer Chris DeLorenzo, designer and developer Nathan Hass and journalist David Tanklefsky. The podcast was created as a means to shine a light on young, creative people forging their own path in a weird world. We chat with the bravest of assorted dream-chasers: musicians, designers, artists, entrepreneurs, writers, yoga teachers and cocktail makers. Be brave is a simple statement that reflects the direction arrow we hope to follow when anxiously navigating the vicissitudes of life. It's a repudiation of the saying &ldquo;to err on the side of caution.&rdquo; When you don't know which way to go, be brave.</p>
  </div>
