          <h4 class="aboutProfiles-gridName">Chris Delorenzo</h4>
          <p class="aboutProfiles-gridText">Chris is a graphic artist and designer breathing and working in Boston. By day he is the lead designer for Johnny Cupcakes, and by night he lends his hand and ideas illustrating for global brands of all kinds like Jameson Irish Whiskey, Lincoln Motor Company, Converse, Sony and more. He likes simple bold lines and the poetry in an image. </p>
        </li>
        <li class="aboutProfiles-gridItem">
          <div class="aboutProfiles-imgMod"><img src="/wp-content/themes/beBrave/static/img/david.jpg" class="aboutProfiles-img"></div>
          <h4 class="aboutProfiles-gridName">David Tanklefsky</h4>
          <p class="aboutProfiles-gridText">David is a writer, journalist, radio broadcaster, musician and sports play-by-play broadcaster. Among his anecdotal claims to fame would be: serving on the jury of a murder trial, interviewing Jerry Seinfeld, announcing the starting lineups at Fenway Park and calling the first perfect game in the history of North Carolina's Coastal Plain League. He was born, lives and works in Boston, Massachusetts. </p>
        </li>
